      "releaseNotes": "Studio Editor\n• Dramatically improved ball flight tracking accuracy and reliability\n• Major performance optimizations across the Studio Editor\n• Export rendering now up to 8× faster\n• Better and faster camera stabilization now up to 10× faster\n• Numerous bug fixes and under-the-hood improvements\n• Powerful editing tools and exciting new features coming soon!",
